Package: snd-hda-codec-cs8409-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, dkms, linux-headers-generic | linux-headers
Description: HDA codec driver for Cirrus Logic CS8409 (DKMS)
 This package provides a kernel module for the Cirrus Logic CS8409
 HDA bridge chip, commonly found in Apple MacBook Pro and iMac systems.
 .
 The module is built using DKMS and will be automatically rebuilt
 when new kernel versions are installed.
 .
 Supported devices include:
  - Apple MacBook Pro (2017-2019)
  - Apple iMac (2017-2020)
  - Dell systems with CS8409/CS42L42
